🤖 **Common notes app mistakes and fixes.**

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| No Room | Use Room database |
| No Flow | Use Flow for data |
| No saving | Use Room insert |
| No error handling | Use try-catch |
| No validation | Validate input |
| No Room setup | Initialize database |

**Fixes:**
